    "The number of n-gram′ in the candidate is represented by Count(ngram 0).",
    "Therefore, the denominator is the number of n-gram among all candidates.",
    "The purpose of A is to prevent gaming problems with evaluation indicators.",
    "The problem with gaming is to prevent optimizing the algorithm for a certain evaluation indicator so that when the human gives a low score, the evaluation index gives a high score.",
